      "file_path": "docker-compose/docker-compose.yml",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 36,
      "message": "The documentation in docker compose readme could mention 'nexus.repository` parameter to generate the image locally with a different name that is not conflicting with onap nexus one:\n\nmvn clean install -Pcps-docker -Dnexus.repository=onap/\n\nor\n\nmvn clean install -Pcps-docker -Dnexus.repository=''\n\nAnd we can set the image name in docker-compose.yml accordingly.",
